g.text: Are you committed to a cloud provider?
->[GCP] : Use Vertex AI Agents or Dialogflow CX
->[Azure] : Use Azure AI Studio or Semantic Kernel
Need profiling and optimization across frameworks?
-> : Reconsider tying to a cloud-native stack for ease of integration
-> : Dialogflow CX or Azure Bot Framework
Primary use case is chat/voice UX?
-> : Use AWS Bedrock or Azure Copilot Stack
-> : Use Vertex AI Agents + Vertex Search
